{
  "stem": "27507.7",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that, what I said before about terror, was now fully there, because we had-- we were driven by those [NON-ENGLISH] or maybe they were Lats, but they were beating the people and beating them with sticks and with whips and driving with screams and shouts so that everybody was walking as fast as they could.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the atmosphere, and I think Jurek, my cousin, who was on my side, got as well few-- a few strokes of the-- being beaten with the-- with the stick.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I not, I think because I was walking in the middle, and I was smaller.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I don't think I got beaten, but my cousin was certainly.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were walking four of us in one row.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That means my cousins, a boy of 18 and the girl of 16 and then me, and then there was my uncle walking on the left-hand side.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was the oldest of us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there was this long street, [GERMAN], which was leading roughly in direction of the umschlagplatz, and it was those big house which were everything was closed.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The windows were closed, because no-- people were afraid to look out when it was happening, you know?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "People were not even coming near the windows.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was like we were already condemned.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were already on the other side, so people didn't even come near the window.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Whoever was there in those houses, they didn't even come-- want to come near the street.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they say, so there were those big houses all empty, and the gates all locked.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were pushed ahead, and one of those gates was, however, open.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
